{"tid":477658,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［失落的皇朝］不滿因航擬削薪津 機師公會籌百萬或12月罷工","createTime":"2017-11-23T08:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T03:26:19.000Z","uid":17822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"045a96f3ffe64ca699e0c40e99a1d848037e3c53","tid":477658,"uid":17822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T08:44:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171123&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57494583\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171123%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57494583&d=vvZaVjXVMljUr7jM103PqDM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=8dfe4f7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171123%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57494583&h=e284e05a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171123&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57494583</a><br />\n聖誕外遊注意！不滿國泰擬削薪津 機師工會籌百萬或12月罷工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/23/164400_ab549db3c99a3c7fbe798306d926bc43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F23%2F164400_ab549db3c99a3c7fbe798306d926bc43.jpg&h=dac42788&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年上半年勁蝕20億元的國泰航空，計劃削減機師每年9億元房屋津貼，料逾千名本地機師會受影響。據了解，機師工會研究在12月採取工業行動，阻止國泰單方面修改僱傭合約，一旦成事將對計劃聖誕期間外遊的市民造成嚴重影響。本報向國泰航空查詢，暫時未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n本報取得一封由機師工會發給會員的電郵，內容是向會員額外徵費，每名會員最多須繳500元，按職級而定，以機師工會現時有約2,000名國泰機師會員為計，最多可籌近百萬元。電郵寫明，該筆款項是一旦採取工業行動時，向受影響的會員提供支援。據《南華早報》報道，機師工會將於下月13至27日進行投票，以決定採取工業行動，料12月29日有結果，但報道引述工會指，不排除由12月14日起隨時罷工<br />\n<br />\n國泰早前在內部公佈節流方案，包括削減機師每年9億元房屋津貼，國泰現時2,500名本地機師將有43%，即約1,070人受影響，希望在2019年達到削減機師成本開支一成的目標，但當時機師工會已警告，國泰不可單方面修改僱傭合約。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/23/164341_13c740ccedd9474bb7a19bbe7fa194cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F23%2F164341_13c740ccedd9474bb7a19bbe7fa194cc.jpg&h=ff92c76c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/23/164247_f758a29c2729b9b4b16766b75983596d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F23%2F164247_f758a29c2729b9b4b16766b75983596d.jpg&h=3e26bc73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39a883d155b213109fd7244273ef28dff1b95f6d","tid":477658,"uid":19654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T08:50:44.000Z","msg":"國泰不知幾想班鬼走<br />\n香港機師人工平一截"},{"pid":"8f43ab299e7be301889e0587aa45bf84cfaa3fdd","tid":477658,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T03:26:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國泰不知幾想班鬼走<br />\n香港機師人工平一截</blockquote><br />\n你應該講清楚係舊制鬼佬嗟"}]}